## Remarks  
<span data-ttu-id="be2a4-212">Se o atual <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo> representa uma definição de método genérico, em seguida:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be2a4-212">If the current <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo> represents a generic method definition, then:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="be2a4-213">`IsGenericMethodDefinition` retorna `true`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be2a4-213">`IsGenericMethodDefinition` returns `true`.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="be2a4-214">Para cada <xref:System.Type> objeto na matriz retornada pelo <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.GetGenericArguments> método:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be2a4-214">For each <xref:System.Type> object in the array returned by the <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.GetGenericArguments> method:</span></span>

      - <span data-ttu-id="be2a4-215">A propriedade <xref:System.Type.IsGenericParameter?displayProperty=nameWithType> retorna `true`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be2a4-215">The <xref:System.Type.IsGenericParameter?displayProperty=nameWithType> property returns `true`.</span></span>

      - <span data-ttu-id="be2a4-216">O <xref:System.Type.DeclaringMethod?displayProperty=nameWithType> retorna atual <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be2a4-216">The <xref:System.Type.DeclaringMethod?displayProperty=nameWithType> returns the current <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo>.</span></span>

      - <span data-ttu-id="be2a4-217">O <xref:System.Type.GenericParameterPosition?displayProperty=nameWithType> propriedade é o mesmo que a posição do <xref:System.Type> objeto na matriz.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be2a4-217">The <xref:System.Type.GenericParameterPosition?displayProperty=nameWithType> property is the same as the position of the <xref:System.Type> object in the array.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be2a4-218">Use o `IsGenericMethodDefinition` propriedade para determinar se os argumentos de tipo atribuídos aos parâmetros de tipo de um método genérico.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be2a4-218">Use the `IsGenericMethodDefinition` property to determine whether type arguments have been assigned to the type parameters of a generic method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be2a4-219">Se os argumentos de tipo tem sido atribuídos, o `IsGenericMethodDefinition` propriedade retorna false, mesmo se alguns dos argumentos de tipo são <xref:System.Type> objetos que representam os parâmetros de tipo de tipos de delimitadores.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be2a4-219">If type arguments have been assigned, the `IsGenericMethodDefinition` property returns false even if some of the type arguments are <xref:System.Type> objects that represent type parameters of enclosing types.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be2a4-220">Por exemplo, considere o seguinte C\#, Visual Basic e o código C++:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be2a4-220">For example, consider the following C\#, Visual Basic, and C++ code:</span></span>

    ```cs
    class C
    {
        T N<T,U>(T t, U u) {...}
        public V M<V>(V v)
        {
            return N<V,int>(v, 42);
        }
    }
    ```

    ```vb
    Class C
        Public Function N(Of T,U)(ByVal ta As T, ByVal ua As U) As T
            ...
        End Function
        Public Function M(Of V)(ByVal va As V ) As V
            Return N(Of V, Integer)(va, 42)
        End Function
    End Class
    ```

    ```cpp
    ref class C
    {
    private:
        generic <typename T, typename U> T N(T t, U u) {...}
    public:
        generic <typename V> V M(V v)
        {
            return N<V, int>(v, 42);
        }
    };
    ```

<span data-ttu-id="be2a4-221">O corpo do método de M contém uma chamada ao método N, especificando o parâmetro de tipo de M e o tipo <xref:System.Int32>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be2a4-221">The method body of M contains a call to method N, specifying the type parameter of M and the type <xref:System.Int32>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be2a4-222">O `IsGenericMethodDefinition` propriedade retorna false para o método `N<V,int>`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be2a4-222">The `IsGenericMethodDefinition` property returns false for method `N<V,int>`.</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="be2a4-223">Embora o método construído de abrir o `N<V,int>` não é encontrado durante a reflexão sobre a classe C, ele deve ser gerado usando <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.MakeGenericMethod%2A> para emitir C como uma classe dinâmica.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be2a4-223">Although the open constructed method `N<V,int>` is not encountered when reflecting over class C, it must be generated using <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.MakeGenericMethod%2A> in order to emit C as a dynamic class.</span></span>


<span data-ttu-id="be2a4-224">Se uma definição de método genérico inclui parâmetros genéricos do tipo declarativo, haverá uma definição de método genérico específicos para cada tipo construído.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be2a4-224">If a generic method definition includes generic parameters of the declaring type, there will be a generic method definition specific to each constructed type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be2a4-225">Por exemplo, considere o seguinte C\# e código do Visual Basic:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be2a4-225">For example, consider the following C\# and Visual Basic code:</span></span>

    ```csharp
    class B<U,V> {}
    class C<T> { public B<T,S> M<S>() {...}}
    ```

    ```vb
    Class B(Of U, V)
    End Class
    Class C(Of T)
        Public Function M(Of S)() As B(Of T, S)
            ...
        End Function
    End Class
    ```

    ```cpp
    generic <typename U, typename V> ref class B {};
    generic <typename T> ref class C
    {
    public:
        generic <typename S> B<T,S>^ M() {...};
    };
    ```

<span data-ttu-id="be2a4-226">O tipo construído `C<int>` (`C(Of Integer)` no Visual Basic), retorna o método genérico M `B<int, S>`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be2a4-226">In the constructed type `C<int>` (`C(Of Integer)` in Visual Basic), the generic method M returns `B<int, S>`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be2a4-227">No tipo aberto `C<T>`, retorna M `B<T, S>`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be2a4-227">In the open type `C<T>`, M returns `B<T, S>`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be2a4-228">Em ambos os casos, o `IsGenericMethodDefinition` propriedade retorna `true` para o <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo> que representa o M.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be2a4-228">In both cases, the `IsGenericMethodDefinition` property returns `true` for the <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo> that represents M.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="be2a4-229">Para obter uma lista de condições invariáveis para termos específicos para métodos genéricos, consulte o <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.IsGenericMethod> propriedade.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be2a4-229">For a list of the invariant conditions for terms specific to generic methods, see the <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.IsGenericMethod> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="be2a4-230">Para obter uma lista de condições invariáveis para outros termos usados na reflexão genérica, consulte o <xref:System.Type.IsGenericType> propriedade.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="be2a4-230">For a list of the invariant conditions for other terms used in generic reflection, see the <xref:System.Type.IsGenericType> property.</span></span>

